notes: |
  `Popup-container--left` left-aligns the popup with the triggering element. Can be used in conjunction with `Popup--down` to make the popup appear below _and_ left-aligned.

  Classes:
  - `.Popup-container--left` as a modifier to `Popup-container`

---


